{
  "career": "programmer",
  "careerName": "程序员",
  "act": 3,
  "actName": "边界：你靠什么做决定",
  "start": "a3_start",
  "_meta": "第三章·边界。需求膨胀/加塞/甩锅(dev=接不接不合理加塞 / test=严重bug上面想放过你卡不卡)+报喜不报忧加重。探针:理性↔共情、讨好↔原则。",
  "nodes": {
    "a3_start": {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "项目进了深水区,需求像滚雪球,越滚越大。\n总有人想让你「通融一下」。",
      "bg": "office_day",
      "effects": { "stress": 3 },
      "choices": [{ "label": "(继续往下)", "next": "a3_dilemma" }]
    },
    "a3_dilemma": {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "这天,一个让你为难的请求摆到面前。",
      "bg": "office_day",
      "effects": {},
      "choices": [
        { "label": "(是一个临时加塞的需求)", "next": "a3_dev", "condition": { "subRole": "dev" } },
        { "label": "(是一个想被放过的 bug)", "next": "a3_test", "condition": { "subRole": "test" } }
      ],
      "note": "★子职业分叉:边界两难。"
    },
    "a3_dev": {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "小林:「就加一个小功能,今晚上线前塞进去呗?」\n这个「一点点」会牵动一大片代码,还没经过评审。",
      "bg": "office_996",
      "effects": { "stress": 4 },
      "choices": [
        { "label": "算了,加班塞进去,别得罪人", "next": "a3_report", "effects": { "performance": 3, "health": -4, "passion": -2 }, "tag": "please", "axes": { "empathy": 2, "risk": 2 } },
        { "label": "顶住,说清风险,这个不能硬塞", "next": "a3_report", "effects": { "san": 3, "skill": 2, "stress": 2 }, "tag": "principle", "axes": { "empathy": -2, "plan": 2 } }
      ]
    },
    "a3_test": {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "你测出一个不致命、但会偶发的 bug。小林劝你:「先放过吧,概率很低,不然赶不上发布。」",
      "bg": "office_996",
      "effects": { "stress": 4 },
      "choices": [
        { "label": "放过吧,别当那个扫兴的人", "next": "a3_report", "effects": { "performance": 2, "san": -3, "passion": -2 }, "tag": "please", "axes": { "empathy": 2, "risk": 2 } },
        { "label": "卡住,记录在案,守住质量线", "next": "a3_report", "effects": { "san": 3, "skill": 2, "stress": 2 }, "tag": "principle", "axes": { "empathy": -2, "plan": 2 } }
      ]
    },
    "a3_report": {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "晚上十点,妈妈发来短信:「最近忙不忙?别太累了。」",
      "bg": "office_996",
      "effects": {},
      "choices": [
        { "label": "「不忙,挺好的。」报喜不报忧", "next": "a3_pantry", "effects": { "san": -2 }, "tag": "report_good_news", "axes": { "empathy": 2 } },
        { "label": "「有点累,但能扛。」说句实话", "next": "a3_pantry", "effects": { "san": 3 }, "tag": "honest", "axes": { "empathy": -1 } }
      ],
      "note": "★报喜不报忧加重。"
    },
    "a3_pantry": {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "茶水间,老陈就着那只枸杞杯泡水。\n他没抬头:「守边界,不是不合群,是还想在这行走得远一点。」",
      "bg": "pantry",
      "effects": { "san": 3, "passion": 2 },
      "choices": [{ "label": "(点点头)", "next": "a3_end" }],
      "note": "★老陈镜像戏:枸杞杯回收+点题「边界」。"
    },
    "a3_end": {
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "回到工位,窗外城市的灯还亮着。\n通融,还是守线?这题没有标准答案。",
      "bg": "office_night",
      "action": "next_act",
      "effects": { "san": 2 },
      "choices": [],
      "note": "★章末 next_act。"
    }
  }
}
